OL,6,FThe next day, they said: "Although the
OL,7,Fspill was very small, we're sorry this
OL,8,Fhappened and that it sadly resulted in
OL,9,Fprecautionary advice being given
OL,10,Fagainst bathing on Exmouth Beach."
OL,12,FHelen Dobby, SWW's head of
OL,13,Fenvironmental performance, was onsite
OL,14,Fin Exmouth on Monday.
OL,16,FShe said: "We are carrying out repairs
OL,17,Fto the burst rising main which we know
OL,18,Fhas been affecting the community.
