OL,6,F"We are working 24 hours a day to make
OL,7,Fsure the repair is fixed quickly and
OL,8,Fis resilient for the future."
OL,10,FShe apologised to customers for the
OL,11,Fdisruption that's been caused.
OL,13,FOn Monday 2 September, SWW said: "We
OL,14,Fhave had spills from our storm
OL,15,Foverflows over the weekend as a result
OL,16,Fof heavy rainfall. Storm overflows are
OL,17,Fpressure relief valves built into our
OL,18,Fnetwork that stop homes and businesses
OL,19,Ffrom flooding during periods of heavy
OL,20,Frain.
