OL,6,FCampaign group Surfers Against Sewage
OL,7,Fhas an interactive map which shows the
OL,8,Fwater quality of popular beaches and
OL,9,Fswimming spots.
OL,11,FFor Dawlish, Budleigh Salterton, and
OL,12,FSidmouth, it said: "Storm sewage has
OL,13,Fbeen discharged from a sewer overflow
OL,14,Fin this location within the past 48
OL,15,Fhours and bathing is not advised today
OL,16,Fdue to the likelihood of reduced water
OL,17,Fquality.
OL,19,FAs for Exmouth, it said: "Risk of
OL,20,Freduced water quality due to sewage."
